column7: Using cElementTree to parse untrusted XML data is known to be vulnerable to XML attacks. Replace cElementTree with the equivalent defusedxml package, or make sure defusedxml.defuse_stdlib() is called.
Using ElementTree to parse untrusted XML data is known to be vulnerable to XML attacks. Replace ElementTree with the equivalent defusedxml package, or make sure defusedxml.defuse_stdlib() is called.
